commitResults.messageTitle: Implement comprehensive logging system for Coinflip application
commitResults.messageBody:
Added a robust logging system to track application behavior and improve debugging:

- Created CoinflipLogger utility class to centralize logging functionality
- Implemented different log levels (INFO, WARNING, SEVERE, FINE)
- Added detailed logging for all major operations (commands, game state changes, file operations)
- Ensured proper exception logging with contextual information

This enhancement improves maintainability and will make future debugging much easier by providing a clear audit trail of application behavior.
